No. 919,

Misc.

New Mexico State Game Commission v. United States Court of Appeals for the Tenth Circuit et al. James A. Maloney, Attorney General of New Mexico, and James E. Sperling, George T. Harris, Jr., and Peter J. Broullire III, Special Assistant Attorneys General, on the motion.

Motion for leave to file petition for writ of mandamus denied.

Mr. Justice Douglas is of the opinion that the motion should be granted.
